OL,4,Cfeel completely safe again' after
OL,5,Cstalker
OL,7,FStrictly Come Dancing head judge
OL,8,FShirley Ballas has said she will
OL,9,F"never feel completely safe again"
OL,10,Fafter being targeted by a stalker who
OL,11,Faccused her of killing a member of her
OL,12,Ffamily.
OL,14,FThe 64-year-old moved her mother to a
OL,15,Fdifferent home and increased security
OL,16,Fmeasures due to harassment by Kyle
OL,17,FShaw, 37, who in February pleaded
OL,18,Fguilty at Liverpool Crown Court to
OL,19,Fstalking Ballas, causing serious harm
OL,20,For distress between August 31, 2017
OL,21,Fand November 29, 2023.
