OL,7,FIn an interview with the Sunday
OL,8,FMirror, Ballas said of the incident:
OL,9,F"I will never feel completely safe
OL,10,Fagain.
OL,12,F"I'm looking around and watching all
OL,13,Fthe time... and life shouldn't have to
OL,14,Fbe like that. That's what he's done to
OL,15,Fme and my family."
