OL,5,Cstalker
OL,7,FBallas discusses the experience in her
OL,8,Fnew memoir Best Foot Forward,
OL,9,Frevealing Shaw followed and confronted
OL,10,Fher elderly mother Audrey in a
OL,11,Fsupermarket, and how she worried he
OL,12,Fwould "put a bomb through the
OL,13,Fletterbox" or "set the house on fire".
OL,15,FShe said Shaw's campaign began when he
OL,16,Fstarted sending her messages on social
OL,17,Fmedia claiming to be the biological
OL,18,Fson of her late brother David, who
OL,19,Fdied of suicide in 2003 aged 44.
