OL,5,Cstalker
OL,7,FThe Wallasey-born dancer added: "The
OL,8,Fmessages he wrote to this little old
OL,9,Flady who has never gotten over the
OL,10,Fdeath of her son, it was very hard.
OL,12,F"As for me, I don't think I've ever
OL,13,Ftravelled by train since, I'm always
OL,14,Flooking over my shoulder. If I go to
OL,15,Fthe park, I never go after six
OL,16,Fo'clock. If I'm walking somewhere, I
OL,17,Fnever have ear plugs in."
