OL,4,Cfeel completely safe again' after
OL,5,Cstalker
OL,7,FShe installed CCTV and an extra alarm
OL,8,Fsystem at her house following the
OL,9,Fincident, and says the BBC gave her
OL,10,Fadditional security while working on
OL,11,FStrictly projects.
OL,13,FBallas said Shaw sent her a picture of
OL,14,Fher house and car on social media, and
OL,15,Fthreatened to turn up at dates on the
OL,16,Fpromotional tour for her debut novel,
OL,17,Fas well as getting her former partner
OL,18,FDanny Taylor's phone number.
